es',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CCmTQW7OebM','https://www.coursera.org/course/contraception',NULL,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:33','2013-04-29 06:43:34','coursera_contraception','Learn about the wide range of contraceptive methods, and the public health implications related to access to information and choices about reproductive health.','Medicine Health & Society'),(896,'Aboriginal Worldviews and Education',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7KcLvOUzx0c','https://www.coursera.org/course/aboriginaled',4,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:33','2013-04-29 06:43:34','coursera_aboriginaled','This course will explore indigenous ways of knowing and how this knowledge can inform education to the benefit of all students.','Humanities  Education'),(897,'Analytical Chemistry / Quantitative Analysis and Analytical Chemistry',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rWyUwM-GwgE','https://www.coursera.org/course/analyticalchem',8,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:34','2013-04-29 06:43:34','coursera_analyticalchem','If chemistry is the science of stuff, then analytical chemistry answers the question: what is it? And how much of it do you have? This advanced chemistry course covers the basics of quantitative analysis and analytical chemistry in a one semester format.','Chemistry'),(898,'An Introduction to the U.S. Food System: Perspectives from Public Health',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5pUQOlTnB2o','https://www.coursera.org/course/foodsys',6,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:34','2013-04-29 06:43:34','coursera_foodsys','Explore how food intersects with public health and the environment as it moves from field to plate.','Health & Society Food and Nutrition'),(899,'Community Change in Public Health',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xxDMpBRv0u8','https://www.coursera.org/course/communitychange',6,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:34','2013-04-29 06:43:34','coursera_communitychange','This course examines the community context of the changes needed to promote the public’s health.','Health & Society'),(900,'Neural Networ