earn how to build these tools in this class.','Computer Science: Systems & Security Engineering'),(943,'Creative, Serious and Playful Science of Android Apps',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6rTbNJsztUU','https://www.coursera.org/course/androidapps101',5,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:35','2013-04-29 06:43:35','coursera_androidapps101','This course introduces the fundamental computer science principles that power today&rsquo;s apps. You will also learn to create your own Android app using Java and standard software development tools.','Computer Science: Software Engineering'),(944,'The Modern World: Global History since 1760',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4lEfKSC1mss','https://www.coursera.org/course/modernworld',15,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:35','2013-04-29 06:43:35','coursera_modernworld','This is a survey of modern history from a global perspective. It begins with the revolutions of the late 1700s, tracks the transformation of the world during the 1800s, and analyzes the cataclysms of last century, concluding with the new phase of world history we are experiencing today.','Humanities '),(945,'How Things Work 1',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wjzZLw0nnyA','https://www.coursera.org/course/howthingswork1',6,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:35','2013-04-29 06:43:35','coursera_howthingswork1','An introduction to physics in the context of everyday objects.','Physics'),(946,'Know Thyself',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yJiur5zyIS8','https://www.coursera.org/course/knowthyself',10,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:35','2013-04-29 06:43:35','coursera_knowthyself','An investigation of the nature and limits of self-knowledge from the viewpoints of philosophy, psychoanalysis, experimental psychology, neuroscience, aesthetics, and Buddhism.  Readings are drawn from classical Western, non-Western, and contemporary sources.','Humanities '),(947,'Grow to Greatness: Smart Growth for Private Businesses, Part I',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vF24j1Eq-jE','https://www.coursera.org/course/g