ast 300 years.','Economics & Finance'),(986,'Exercise Physiology: Understanding the Athlete Within',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uHaT7geVoQI','https://www.coursera.org/course/exphys',6,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_exphys','Learn about the physiological responses to acute and chronic exercise and their relevance for athletic performance.','Medicine Biology & Life Sciences'),(987,'Passion Driven Statistics',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7l070-WFb5Q','https://www.coursera.org/course/pdstatistics',6,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_pdstatistics','With existing data, you will develop skills in data analysis and basic statistics by exploring your own research question.','Statistics and Data Analysis'),(988,'Introduction to Pharmacy',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAc_1TeVoYQ','https://www.coursera.org/course/intropharma',7,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_intropharma','This course is a survey of the profession of pharmacy including its history, evolving scope of practice, ethical foundations, regulation, educational and career opportunities, and more. We will also explore topics relating to medication use and drug development.','Medicine Health & Society'),(989,'Principles of Public Health',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zQqwww_DOgs','https://www.coursera.org/course/publichealth',NULL,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_publichealth','Principles of Public Health introduces the major concepts and principles of public health and the determinants of health status in communities. Emphasizes the ecological model that focuses on the linkages and relationships among multiple natural and social determinants affecting health.','Medicine Health & Society'),(990,'Generation Rx: The Science Behind Prescription Drug Abuse',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=exOYbv1QYWw','https://www.coursera.org/course/genrx',6,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_genrx','Think that a prescription medication must be safer than a “street drug”? Think again. Investigate the epidemic rise of prescription drug abuse and use science to debunk commonly held misconceptions regarding this phenomenon.','Medicine Health & Society'),(991,'The Ancient Greeks',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2k9VQhMvWd4','https://www.coursera.org/course/ancientgreeks',7,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_ancientgreeks','This is a survey of ancient Greek history from the Bronze Age to the death of Socrates in 399 BCE. Along with studying the most important events and personalities, we will consider broader issues such as political and cultural values and methods of historical interpretation. ','Humanities '),(992,'Modern European Mysticism and Psychological Thought',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/mysticthought',NULL,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_mysticthought','The course will examine the psychological thought of the modern mystical traditions in Europe. We shall focus on two topics with wider cultural implications: The soul and the heart. ','Humanities '),(993,'Synapses, Neurons and Brains ',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SO7gq972SJ8','https://www.coursera.org/course/bluebrain',9,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_bluebrain','You will become intimately acquainted with the operational principles of neuronal “life-ware” (synapses, neurons and the networks that they form) as well as with recent ideas about how the dynamics of these networks generate the “neuronal code.”  As an aperitif we will highlight present brain-excitements and for dessert we will discuss the future of brain research\n','Biology & Life Sciences'),(994,'Coding the Matrix: Linear Algebra through Computer Science Applications',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IWugXcWpfoM','https://www.coursera.org/course/matrix',8,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:36','2013-04-29 06:43:36','coursera_matrix'