c courses.  The only prerequisite is a basic knowledge of how to read musical notation.','Music, Film, and Audio'),(1071,'Drug Discovery, Development & Commercialization ',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pJdVi_sLzh8','https://www.coursera.org/course/drugdiscovery',9,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:39','2013-04-29 06:43:40','coursera_drugdiscovery','Students will learn the process of drug discovery and development through specific examples of case studies to better understand the issues facing the challenges of delivering a new drug on the market. At the completion of this course you will be able to have a better understanding of how a small or large molecule becomes a pharmaceutical drug.','Medicine Biology & Life Sciences'),(1072,'Social Epidemiology',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rm8zQS3VbjQ','https://www.coursera.org/course/socialepi',7,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:39','2013-04-29 06:43:40','coursera_socialepi','Social epidemiology is about how a society makes people sick and/or healthy. We address not only the identification of new disease risk factors (e.g., deficient social capital) but also how well-known exposures (e.g., cigarette smoking, lead paint, health insurance) emerge and are maintained by the social system.','Health & Society Social Sciences'),(1073,'Statistical Molecular Thermodynamics',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tOEudSv6PtY','https://www.coursera.org/course/thermodynamics',9,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:39','2013-04-29 06:43:40','coursera_thermodynamics','This introductory physical chemistry course examines the connections between molecular properties and the behavior of macroscopic chemical systems.','Chemistry'),(1074,'Interprofessional Healthcare Informatics',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZGiLIDrpZ-0','https://www.coursera.org/course/newwayhealthcare',10,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:39','2013-04-29 06:43:40','coursera_newwayhealthcare','This course examines the implications of informatics for practice, in nursing, public health, and healthcare in