ULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:42','coursera_latinamericanculture','This course seeks to interest students in the Latin American culture by studying it from multiple perspectives.','Humanities  Social Sciences'),(1145,'Einführung in Computer Vision',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/compvision',NULL,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_compvision','Dieser Kurs vermittelt einen Überblick über die Grundlagen des Maschinellen Sehens an Hand der Extraktion von 3D-Information aus dem Stereokamerabild einer Szene.','Computer Science: Artificial Intelligence'),(1146,'Continuidad y desarrollo de la empresa familiar',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X1zhDLEbSVA','https://www.coursera.org/course/empresafamiliar',6,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_empresafamiliar','¿Cuál es la importancia de las empresas familiares en el mundo?, ¿cómo garantizar su continuidad y permanencia?, ¿cómo mejorar la comunicación entre sus miembros? y ¿cómo lograr sucesiones exitosas? Este curso brinda estas respuestas a través de la identificación de estrategias para la profesionalización de las empresas familiares.','Economics & Finance Business & Management Social Sciences'),(1147,'Linear and Integer Programming',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/linearprogramming',NULL,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_linearprogramming','This course will cover the very basic ideas in optimization. Topics include the basic theory and algorithms behind linear and integer linear programming along with some of the important applications. We will also explore the theory of convex polyhedra using linear programming.\n','Computer Science: Theory'),(1148,'Conditions of War and Peace',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/warandpeace',4,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_warandpeace','This course aims to nail down some of the basic issues that had been argued in the current research on peace and security. ','Social Sciences'),(1149,'From the Big Bang to Dark Energy',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/bigbang',4,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_bigbang','This course will cover the various topics on the discoveries about how the Universe evolved in 13.7 billion years since the Big Bang. ','Physics'),(1150,'The Diversity of Exoplanets',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/extrasolarplanets',5,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_extrasolarplanets','The course will provide an overview of the knowledge acquired during the past 20 years in the domain of exoplanets. It will review the different detection methods, their limitations, and the information provided on the orbital system and the planet itself, and how this information is helping our understanding of planet formation.','Physics'),(1151,'Fundamentals of Digital Image and Video Processing',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/digital',12,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_digital','In this class you will learn the basic principles and tools used to process images and videos, and how to apply them in solving practical problems of commercial and scientific interests.  ','Information, Tech & Design Engineering Computer Science: Artificial Intelligence'),(1152,'Introduction to Environmental Law and Policy',1,1,NULL,'https://www.coursera.org/course/environlaw',8,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_environlaw','Interested in learning about how the law analyzes issues and resolves disputes involving pollution, natural resources, endangered species, environmental justice, and sustainable development?  Professor Hornstein will guide you through these issues, and more, in this course.','Law'),(1153,'Physics 1 for Physical Science Majors',1,1,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AfdeGHfwBpM','https://www.coursera.org/course/physics1',NULL,NULL,'2013-04-29 06:43:42','2013-04-29 06:43:43','coursera_physics1',